  [Text] Beijing, June 13 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Premier Li Peng 
today congratulated the Organization of African Unity (OAU) on 
its 30th summit which opened today in Tunis. 
  In a message sent to the summit, Li Peng said the birth of 
new South Africa signified the victory accomplished by the OAU 
and all African people in the political field. 
  But Li also expressed the concern over the on-going 
